high_descs: Move forward and face the counter to your right.
Pick up the knife on the counter in front of you.
Turn around and face the microwave on top of the stove in front of you.
Open the microwave, slice the potato inside and close the microwave again.
Turn around and face the fridge to your right.
Place the knife in the fridge in front of you and close it.
Turn around and face the microwave on top of the stove on your left.
Open the the microwave, take out a potato slice from the inside and close the microwave.
Turn around and face the fridge on your right.
Open the fridge, place the potato inside, close it, take the potato out and close the fridge again.
Turn around and head towards the sink in front of you.
Place the potato slice in the sink in front of you.
anns.task_desc: Place a cold potato slice in the sink.

high_descs: Turn right and go to the counter.
Pick up a knife on the counter.
Turn around and go to the microwave.
Cut the potato in the microwave.
Turn around and go to the refrigerator.
Put the knife in the refrigerator.
Turn around and go to the microwave.
Take a potato slice out of the microwave.
Turn and go to the refrigerator.
Put the potato slice in the refrigerator. Take the potato slice out of the refrigerator.
Turn around and go to the sink.
Put the potato in the sink.
anns.task_desc: Chill a potato slice in the refrigerator.

high_descs: Go forward to the counter, hang a right and go to the counter.
Pick up the big knife that is on the counter to your left.
Turn to the left, go forward, turn to the right and go forward to the microwave.
Open the microwave, use the knife to cut the potato inside the microwave into slices.
Turn around and go forward, then hang a right and go to the fridge.
Open the fridge, put the knife in the fridge, close the door.
Turn around and go forward, then hang a left and go to the microwave.
Open the microwave, pick up a slice of potato, close the microwave.
Turn around and go forward, hang a right and go to the fridge.
Put the potato in the fridge to get cold, then remove the potato from the fridge.
Turn around and go forward to the sink.
Put the cold potato in the sink.
anns.task_desc: Put a cold slice of potato in a sink.

high_descs: Turn to your right then walk straight to the far right of the counter
Pick up the knife on the left side of the counter beside the spoon
Turn to your right then head to the microwave above the stove
Open the microwave and slice the potato inside beside the mug, then close the microwave
Turn around to your left then walk towards the fridge on your right
Open the fridge put inside the knife then close the door
Turn to your right, then to your left and face the microwave
Open the microwave and pick up the slice potato inside then close the microwave
Turn around to your left walk straight to the fridge
Open the fridge, then put in the potato slice in and out then close the fridge
Turn to your right then head to the sink
Put the potato on the sink
anns.task_desc: Put the slice potato from the fridge going to the sink

high_descs: turn to your right and go all the way to the end of the countertop where utensils are sitting on the counter
pick up the sharp knife with a yellow handle
turn back around and carry the knife to the stove area
open then close the microwave door
turn around and go left towards the black fridge
place the knife on the shelf inside the fridge
turn around go back to the microwave, open the door
remove a slice of potato from the microwave
take the potato slice back to the black fridge
place the potato slice in the fridge and chill it for a few seconds; remove the slice from the fridge
turn around and carry the chilled slice of potato to the sink directly in front of you
place the potato slice in the sink in the right front corner
anns.task_desc: Place a chilled potato slice in the sink

high_descs: turn right towards the table
pick up the knife
turn around and head for the oven
slice the potato inside the oven
turn left towards the fridge
place the knife inside the fridge
turn right towards the oven
take out a slice
turn left towards the fridge
place it to cool and then take it out
turn around and head for the sink
drop the slice in the sink
